nodes.text: Julian Kwasneski is credited in the sound departments of Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic, Star Wars: Republic Commando, LEGO Star Wars II: The Original Trilogy, Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords, Star Wars: Force Commander, Star Wars: X-Wing vs. TIE Fighter, the Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace game, and the Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith game.
